<tr>
<td><a id='downspeedf'></a><a href='#downspeedf'>downspeedf</a><p class='ar'>[network_interface]</p></td>
<td>Download speed in KiB with one decimal place. <p class='ex'>${downspeedf eth0}</p></td>
