<tr>
<td><a id='head'></a><a href='#head'>head</a><p class='ar'>logfile lines [next_check]</p></td>
<td>Displays first N lines of supplied text file. The file is checked every <q>next_check</q> update. If next_check is not supplied, Conky defaults to 2. Max of 30 lines can be displayed, or until the <a href='#text_buffer_size'>text_buffer_size</a> is filled. See ${<a href='#tail'>tail</a>} for end of file. <p class='ex'>${head ~/sample.log 5 3}</p></td>
